{"tid":1120714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逸東邨15歲少年墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-04-23T00:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T13:48:13.000Z","uid":3090,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b597cc4ea37c2daebaa2649a146c5098a953ee7","tid":1120714,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hy2Z7f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhy2Z7f8.png&h=3bbb5f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n東涌逸東邨祿逸樓，下午5時許，15歲姓李男少年由高處墮下，倒卧大廈對開。救護員接報到場，將墮樓少年送往北大嶼山醫院搶救，至下午5時40分證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方未有發現遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，懷疑他從上址一天台墮下，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台"},{"pid":"930d4a7ef1e8bf454f0e960bb7f255a23a793580","tid":1120714,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"又係逸東邨"},{"pid":"119ab84f6ad9b827ccad8f6990d68e513e1779f9","tid":1120714,"uid":176063,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:26:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50c31df67e29c3ab0a73d01fa76dc8830a9c9f68","tid":1120714,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411f4cb08a7dda88881a5318656a8a040b43f277","tid":1120714,"uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"養兒防老受害者大聯盟 +1"},{"pid":"c82f52ca766d75be36304c5d60282f4aa0a441f5","tid":1120714,"uid":75994,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"逸東9成係支畜人,無所謂啦"},{"pid":"b2979cc6227fb936e96ba17f126c9e6d53b0faa3","tid":1120714,"uid":22553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTi